flowchart TD
    A[Nurse manager opens spreadsheet] --> B[List shifts to fill<br/>days, nights, weekends]
    B --> C[Check each nurse:<br/>hours, skills, time-off, law limits]
    C --> D{Conflicts?<br/>double-booked,<br/>overtime, gaps}
    D -->|Yes| E[Manually shuffle by hand]
    E --> C
    D -->|No| F[Publish schedule]
    F --> G{Someone calls in sick}
    G -->|Yes| E
    G -->|No| H[Schedule holds this week]

    style A fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1565C0
    style E fill:#FFEBEE,stroke:#C62828
    style H fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#2E7D32
